<TEXT>
<P>
Are two of the prerequisites for participation in the game show "Win, Lose or 
Draw" that one should be devoid of all drawing ability and possess absolutely 
no knowledge of the geography of the world? On a recent show, the performance 
of a young female rock star was nothing short of pathetic. On the whole, I find 
the show an embarrassment as the celebrities' and contestants' deficiencies are 
revealed before thousands of viewers. What schools have these people attended? 
</P>
<P>
J. M. Jackson, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
