I applaud Gillespie for trying to fight the lawyers, educate the legislators, 
tolerate the crusading, immature professional "consumerists" and reform the 
insurance companies. Anyone who has had a claim against an insurance company 
knows insurance reforms are needed, but the insurance companies should not be 
