Chefs, Ken Frank, right, Jonathon Waxman, back, Mark Peel, middle, Michael 
McCarty, front. ; Photo, COLOR, (Cover), Wolfang Puck. Jim Mendenhall / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
