HUNGARY; POLAND -- FOREIGN AID -- EUROPE; HUNGARY -- FOREIGN AID -- EUROPE; 
EUROPEAN ECONOMIC SUMMIT CONFERENCE; SUMMIT CONFERENCES; GOVERNMENT REFORM; 
EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES; BUSH, GEORGE; CHINA -- MARTIAL LAW; CHINA -- FOREIGN AID; 
DRUG TRAFFICKING; ENVIRONMENT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
