ANNIVERSARIES; TRW INC; MCDONNELL DOUGLAS ASTRONAUTICS CO; ROCKWELL 
INTERNATIONAL; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- ORANGE COUNTY; PROJECT APOLLO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
